ActPilotage Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Laurentian Pilotage Tariff Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the LAURENTIAN PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS in order to increase in tariff rates which will allow the Authority to continue to operate on a self-sustaining financial basis by imposing fair and reasonable tariffs that will allow it to provide efficient pilotage services and ensure navigation safety.
